name: Sightseeing Tours
description:
Trying to figure out what to do in Key West?

Enhance your Florida Keys vacation with an interactive road trip excursion Up The Keys! Visit several of the best islands in the Florida Keys and learn the history, culture, ecology, and legends of these extraordinary islands. Travel along the Overseas Highway and visit the premium attractions in the Keys, such as Aquarium Encounters and Dolphin Research Center. Get up close to the wildlife as if you're on a safari. Look for the endangered Key Deer, alligators, and more! Of the many things to do in Key West, one of these Florida Keys tours from Key West Florida are something you shouldn't miss! It's eco-tourism at its best as they travel in small groups of up to 13 for the day. They will pick you and your group up at Oceans Edge Key West and private charter packages are available.
